Download History is a straightforward Chrome extension that allows you to quickly and easily download your browsing history to a CSV file. This tool is perfect for those who want to keep a record of their web activity for personal archiving or analysis. With Download History, you can retrieve your entire browsing history with just one click, without any modifications or data collection.

Features Include:

Simple Interface: A clean, user-friendly interface that makes downloading your history effortless.

Privacy First: No data collection—what you browse stays private, and only you have access to your history.

Instant Download: Get a comprehensive CSV file of your browsing history in moments.

Whether you're a researcher, a data enthusiast, or just someone keen on digital organization, Download History is a solution to back up your online journeys. Install now and take control of your browsing data!
